OL,4,CCovid: Hospital visits ban
OL,5,Csoul-destroying, says patient
OL,6, A woman in hospital for more than 10
OL,7, weeks and unable to have visitors due
OL,8, to Covid rules said the loneliness has
OL,9, been "soul-destroying".
OL,11,FMargaret Evans, 86, from Nefyn,
OL,12,FGwynedd, said she felt "torn away from
OL,13,Fthe world" with a ban on visitors at
OL,14,FYsbyty Alltwen, Tremadog.
OL,16,FBut another nearby community hospital
OL,17,Fhas allowed visits in its garden.
OL,19,FOfficials said visits had been allowed
OL,20,Fin exceptional cases and revised rules
OL,21,Fwould allow more visits by appointment.
